      <td><strong><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/29567165-atomic-design">Atomic Design</a></strong> - This book introduces a methodology for thinking of our UIs as thoughtful hierarchies, discusses the qualities of effective pattern libraries, and showcases techniques to transform your team’s design and development workflow. <a href="http://atomicdesign.bradfrost.com/table-of-contents/">Free to read online</a></td>
