<h3 id="communities">Communities</h3>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p><a href="https://www.iainstitute.org/">Information Architecture Institute</a> - A nonprofit organization of volunteers with a singular focus: to make the world’s information clearer and easier to use by improving how people learn, practice and teach Information Architecture (IA).</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p><a href="https://ixda.org/">Interaction Design Association</a> - Global community of people who share an interest in interaction design.</p>
