  </li>
  <li>
    <p><a href="https://collectui.com/">CollectUI</a> - Daily inspiration collected from daily ui archive and beyond. Hand picked, updating daily.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p><a href="https://uimovement.com/">UI Movement</a> - UI Movement is a community of design enthusiasts who share and discuss the most interesting and unique UI designs.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p><a href="http://inspirationui.com/">Inspiration UI</a> - Inspiration UI  is a community that aims to provide the best design resources for those who create for the web.</p>
